🧠 What is Deployment?

Deployment means **publishing your application on the internet** so users can access it.

Example:

```
Localhost → Production Server → Public Website
```

Before deployment:

```
http://localhost:5173
```

After deployment:

```
https://myreactapp.vercel.app
```

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

🔷 Production Build

Before deploying a React app you must create a **production build**.

```bash
npm run build
```

This creates a **build/dist folder** containing optimized files.

✔ Minified JavaScript
✔ Optimized assets
✔ Faster performance

