🚀 1️⃣ Deploying on Vercel (Recommended ⭐)

Vercel is the easiest platform for React apps.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Steps

1️⃣ Push project to GitHub

2️⃣ Go to:

[https://vercel.com](https://vercel.com)

3️⃣ Click **Import Project**

4️⃣ Select GitHub repository

5️⃣ Click **Deploy**

---

After deployment:

```
https://your-project.vercel.app
```

✔ Automatic builds
✔ Free SSL
✔ CI/CD support

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

🚀 2️⃣ Deploying on Netlify

Netlify is another popular hosting platform.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

 Steps

1️⃣ Build the project

```bash
npm run build
```

2️⃣ Go to:

[https://netlify.com](https://netlify.com)

3️⃣ Drag & drop the **build/dist folder**

Netlify automatically deploys it.

---

Example URL:

```
https://my-react-app.netlify.app
```

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

🚀 3️⃣ Deploying with GitHub Pages

Good for portfolio projects.

---

Install gh-pages

```bash
npm install gh-pages --save-dev
```

---

Add to package.json

```json
"homepage": "https://username.github.io/project-name"
```

---

Add scripts

```json
"scripts": {
  "deploy": "gh-pages -d build"
}
```

---

Deploy

```bash
npm run deploy
```

Your site will be live at:

```
https://username.github.io/project-name
```

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

🚀 4️⃣ Deploying with Firebase Hosting

Install Firebase CLI:

```bash
npm install -g firebase-tools
```

Login:

```bash
firebase login
```

Initialize project:

```bash
firebase init
```

Deploy:

```bash
firebase deploy
```

